      "content": "i dont even know why im talking to u lol. everything is just so heavy right now. people at school and online... they wont stop. it feels like everywhere i look i'm just being mocked. i cant even go to my room without feeling like everyone is watching and judging me. i just want everything to go quiet. i just want the noise to stop.",
